    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>The making of holes through an object; may be done purposefully, either when the object is made or later, or may be the result of natural processes. Having a hole, as a result of the drilling process.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
